quran[36]{c,v,t}:
  26,192,And that it truly is descent (E) (from) Lord (of) the creations all together/(universes)
  26,193,"The Soul/Spirit , the faithful/loyal , descended with it"
  26,194,On your heart/mind to be (E) from the warners/givers of notice
  26,195,With a clear/evident Arabic tongue/language/speech
  26,196,And that it truly is in (E) the first`s/beginner`s Books
  26,197,"Was not an evidence/sign/verse (to) be for them, that Israel`s sons` and daughters` learned ones/knowledgeable know it? (Was not an evidence for them that the Israelites` scholars know of it)"
  26,198,And even if We descended it on (to) some (of) the non-Arabs/Persians
  26,199,"So he read it on (to) them, (and) they were not with it believing"
  26,200,As/like that We entered it in the criminals`/sinners` hearts/minds
  26,201,"They do not believe with it until they see the torture, the painful"
  26,202,"So it comes to them suddenly/unexpectedly, and (while) they are not feeling/knowing/sensing"
  26,203,"So they say: \"Are we delayed"
  26,204,Are (they) with Our torture hastening/urging
  26,205,So did you see if We gave them long life/made them enjoy years
  26,206,Then came to them what they were being promised
  26,207,What they were being made to enjoy did not enrich/suffice (benefit) from them
  26,208,"And We did not destroy from a village/urban city, except for it (are) warners/givers of notice"
  26,209,"A remembrance/reminder, and We were not unjust/oppressive"
  26,210,And the devils did not descend with it
  26,211,"And (it) should not (be) for them, and they are not able"
  26,212,"That they truly are from the hearing/listening , they are being separated/isolated (E)"
  26,213,"So do not call with God another god, so you be/become from the tortured ones"
  26,214,And warn/give notice (to) your father`s near relations/tribe the nearest/closest
  26,215,And be lenient/comforting your wing/side (be kind) to who followed you from the believers
  26,216,"So if they disobeyed you, so say: \"That I am innocent/renouncing from what you make/do"
  26,217,"And rely/depend on the glorious/mighty, the merciful"
  26,218,Who sees you when you stand/get up
  26,219,And your turning in (between) the prostrating
  26,220,"That He truly is the hearing/listening, the knowledgeable"
  26,221,"Do I inform you, on (to) whom the devils descend"
  26,222,"(They) descend on (to) every/each liar/falsifier, sinner/criminal"
  26,223,"They listen attentively the hearing/listening , and most of them (are) lying/denying"
  26,224,"And the poets, (only) the misguiding/failing follow them"
  26,225,Do you not see that they truly are in every/each valley they wander about confused
  26,226,And that they truly say what they do not make/do
  26,227,"Except those who believed and made/did the correct/righteous deeds and they remembered/mentioned God much, and they became victorious from after what they were caused injustice to/oppressed ; and those who caused injustice/oppressed will know which place of return , they return to"